article.description: — Quincy Olivari had a career-high 35 points as Rice defeated Houston Baptist 90-79 on Tuesday.
article.headline: Olivari scores 35 to lift Rice past Houston Baptist 90-79
article.linkText: Olivari scores 35 to lift Rice past Houston Baptist 90-79
article.story: HOUSTON -- — Quincy Olivari had a career-high 35 points as Rice defeated Houston Baptist 90-79 on Tuesday. Olivari made 6 of 9 3-pointers. Chris Mullins had 14 points for Rice (5-1). Riley Abercrombie added 11 points. Pedro Castro had 19 points for the Huskies (1-5). Darius Lee added 13 points and Za-Ontay Boothman had 12 points. ------ For more AP college basketball coverage: https://apnews.com/Collegebasketball and http://twitter.com/AP--Top25 ------ This was generated by Automated Insights, http://www.automatedinsights.com/ap, using data from STATS LLC, https://www.stats.com
